lead_paragraph: Sevilla coach Jorge Sampaoli agreed that he deserved to be sent off for dissent during his team's controversial 3-1 defeat by Juventus in the Champions League on Tuesday.

headline.print_headline: Sevilla Coach Sampaoli Agreed With His Own Sending-Off
